@node "winb" "WindowBar"

@{fg shine} WindowBar@{fg text}

           If you've ever seen a PC with the start menu you'll know what this
 program is like stright away. Winbar is a little program that sits at the bottom
 of your screen with all your files ready to be selected. This is a very useful
 program and is easy to set up but there are some faults in it which really let
 it down. First of all the shutdown doesn't work and just makes your computer
 lock up, so once you've run Winbar you can't quit it. The next problem is you
 can't get out of the section of the menu without clicking on the WB, this isn't
 a major problem but it does become anoying after a while. Winbar is a very nice,
 useful program but you'll have to put up with the bugs to use it.

